###Block: Dwarf Abilities
# Ability Name								Clear Description	Description
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Defensive Training ~ Dwarf.MOD	DESC:.CLEAR		DESC:Dwarves get a +4 dodge bonus to AC against monstes of the giant type.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Greed.MOD					DESC:.CLEAR		DESC:Dwarves treat Appraise as a class skill when attempting to determine the price of nonmagical goods that contain precious metals and gemstones.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Hatred ~ Dwarf.MOD			DESC:.CLEAR		DESC:Dwarves receive a +1 bonus on attack rolls against humanoid creatures of the orc and goblin subtype due to special training against these hated foes.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Hearty.MOD					DESC:.CLEAR		DESC:Dwarves receive a +2 racial bonus on saving throws against poison, spells, and spell-like abilities.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Keen Senses ~ Dwarf.MOD		DESC:.CLEAR		DESC:Dwarves receive a +2 bonus on taste- and touch-based Perception skill checks.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Steady.MOD					DESC:.CLEAR		DESC:Dwarves never have their speed reduced by armor or encumbrance.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Stability.MOD				DESC:.CLEAR		DESC:Dwarves receive a +4 bonus to their combat maneuver bonus when resisting a bull rush or trip attempt while standing on the ground.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Stonecunning.MOD				DESC:.CLEAR		DESC:Dwarves treat any Craft and Profession skill related to stone as a class skill. In addition, they receive a +2 bonus on Perception skill checks to notice unusual stonework, such as traps and hidden doors located in stone walls or f loors. They receive a check to notice such features whenever they pass within 10 feet of them, regardless of whether or not they are actively looking.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Weapon Familiarity ~ Dwarf.MOD	DESC:.CLEAR		DESC:Dwarves are proficient with battleaxes, handaxes, and warhammers, and treat any weapon with the word
